Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是都说了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被“红世之徒”给吞食了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红世的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个怪物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是“磷子”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“红世之徒”的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“磷子”收集 \N“徒”就吞食
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我那时应该被你所救了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是要救你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是碰巧的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“红世之徒”或“磷子”来到这个世界并非第一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上都很自然地发生着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说真正的你在遇到它之前就已经被吞食了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正 “火炎”还很亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还不是太久之前的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必担心 会慢慢燃烧殆尽的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧殆尽是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说作为torch的你会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在还好好地站在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那个 “红世”什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你被“封绝”给圈住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“封绝”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说那个像火之墙的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确来说是墙里的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在那里世界的“流动的因果”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被暂时地切断了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:05:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不会知道到底发生什么事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且“徒”根本就不是人那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为被吞食了“存在” 那个人就会变成从来就没有过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会剩下些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了就会变成从来就没有过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也能看得见的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个很小的torch
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火…好小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就在眼前消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是用torch的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“存在”消失的话 世界失去平衡就会变得很糟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你走着就突然就消溶的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.51,0:05:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会受到你消失的冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.05,0:06:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若使大地冰冻而慢慢地消溶的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到的冲击就会被缓和的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把冰冻看作是torch就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,torch将慢慢的消耗存在力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在“消灭”的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影响就会降到最小的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你还不能理解的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.39,0:06:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的我都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该如何反应才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…坂井悠二竟然已经都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在站在这里的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个要五个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:06:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜瓜面包 吃的东西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这个我当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就别问了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想跟着我到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家就在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的会消失吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在做梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别老问我同样的问题好不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的事情竟然是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太残酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是现实？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 脑袋转不过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情竟然吃着甜瓜面包说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 吵死了 吵死了 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有什么想问啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是flamehaze
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,flamehaze 是为了将吞食\N“存在力”的“红世之徒”歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算把很多“torch”派出
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始终也只是一时的应对办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于“存在”被肆意滥捕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而导致的世界的危机这个事实是不会变的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,flamehaze
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用“磷子”的“徒” 好像仍然还在这座城市里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听那个“磷子”的口气 大概是个相当大的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.34,0:08:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不惧我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.89,0:08:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还有一个理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个mystes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊看啊 玛利亚奴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么的美丽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将在这座城市获得永远 再过不久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 可是…那个flamehaze
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘 不要提起那个败兴的名字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好享受现在这段美好的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这种话我可不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所需要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小悠 今天你还真悠闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不会吧 都这个时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠竟然睡过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且昨天一回来马上就睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪里不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是偶尔啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.77,0:10:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没事 妈妈不是torch
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天爸爸打电话回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金周果然还是不能回到日本
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是知道我已经都死了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 大概他们会认为最初就没有孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:11:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他说暑假一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.78,0:11:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起让他们伤心 还是最初就没有比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的坂井悠二…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我现在担心什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的坂井悠二的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝望和不安倒是理所当然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.03,0:11:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班主任对时间很严格的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你走了啊 路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起去找“红世之徒”我还是看住你来得快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是个相当少见的torch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来昨天那个“磷子”说我是mystes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你还记得真清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,mystes就是“红世之徒”作成的\N注入了“宝具”或者力量的torch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:17.00,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝具：能引起各种现象的器物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“宝具”？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个torch燃烧殆尽的话 身体里的东西会转移到其它上面去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说白了就是会移动的宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.69,0:12:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是那个“宝具”自己跑到你身去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人恐怕会在你燃烧殆尽之前 来抢走的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,torch中的mystes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我所想的都是作为坂井悠二要考虑的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是残留的渣 这是当然的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:12:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 那个时候平井同学她也 …
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰好小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下一点儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是被袭击就昨天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是被吃掉太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的“磷子”们乱吃了一气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.95,0:13:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学 平井同学 早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是平井同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经快支撑不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能变回以前吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的 因为是残留的渣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人已经都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样实在是太残酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 那个不是人 只是torch而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:13:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学 快跑吧 要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点儿 打起精神来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算 什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都告诉他了是变不回来了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是在他人身上 感受得到自身的存在感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学竟然要消失 不会是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池同学他有女朋友了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 坂井 严重迟到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井一个×
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 平井同学也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是一起来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:14:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了你 真是少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:14:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都没有看平井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去会渐渐失去存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而被忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学 中午有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井 你午饭要买什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去小卖部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.09,0:15:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和池一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 池 行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女生是我们班的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在这儿了 当然是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个呢 那个新的补习班的老师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然就是村田的大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池 你今天要去补习班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 今天没课
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那放学后我们去车站前玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也比较闲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.67,0:16:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 决定了 平井同学 池他也要去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然说到池 她还是有些反应的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.19,0:16:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说只有一点儿 但或许能够\N变回昨天那样的平井同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 池 再靠近点儿 我拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉相当不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像有些碍事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 平井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我说你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面我们去玩儿什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去玩抓玩偶机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学 和池玩儿对战游戏怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池和平井同学玩儿会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太活跃了 给我安分一点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处跑来跑去的麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能这样说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你很同情她 那也只是个torch而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失的命运是改变不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 要是大家不忘记平井同学的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你说不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.38,0:18:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种白痴torch我还是第一次见到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 池 平井同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？平井同学是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学啊 不是和你在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 难道说平井同学已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 好像刚才出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 是出去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说我过关了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池 你为什么这么漠不关心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好想想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我们还三个一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.56,0:18:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学她 平井同学她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池同学他有女朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 坂井 你怎么了 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是池的错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是torch
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.34,0:18:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我去找平井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:18:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了 那小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学 你还没有消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 千万不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 都说了别到处跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个怪怪的torch啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急躁的家伙到处都有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 池他说有事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是里面没有我的话 你跟池很般配的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢这景色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 所以你来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学 明天带池来这儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里…和池…所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是torch
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:20:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会这样消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残留的渣总会燃烧殆尽的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不会记得其存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后什么也不会留下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.22,0:21:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学存在过 喜欢过池
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫过平井由香里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是绝对存在过的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.06,0:21:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道自己叫坂井悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是torch
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样我也是坂井悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也同样存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.29,0:21:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是flamehaze
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只是这样而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种意义上其实和torch也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再说什么“只有”这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为本来就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.23,0:21:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是torch 我只是flamehaze
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.09,0:21:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.96,0:22:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.54,0:22:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.58,0:22:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是flamehaze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.75,0:22:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又这样说了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.74,0:22:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 吵死了 吵死了 需要什么名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.43,0:22:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和别的flamehaze区别的时候 就叫贽殿遮那的flamehaze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.43,0:22:22.19,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贽殿遮那：被称为“炎发灼眼的杀戮者”所持的大太刀在打倒了\N号称“史上最恶Mystes”的传说中的怪物“天目一个”之后取得。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.63,0:22:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贽殿遮那？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.35,0:22:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是她所持大太刀的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贽殿遮那
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.08,0:22:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就叫夏娜了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.08,0:22:31.87,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日文中“夏娜”和“遮那”同音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今开始我就这样叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.32,0:22:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是夏娜 不只是什么flamehaze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.73,0:22:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不只是什么torch
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.77,0:22:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是坂井悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.81,0:22:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 她的名字是我给取的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那天开始 炎发灼眼的framhaze就成了夏娜

